These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, zombie, mystery
Transport: snowmobile, helicopter, car, trike
1. Transport:helicopter is on the left of Transport:snowmobile##1
2. Movie-Genre:crime == Transport:trike##1
3. Transport:car is on the right of Transport:snowmobile##1
4. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Transport:trike##1
5. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Transport:snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | mystery | zombie | musical | crime   |
| Transport   | helicopter  | snowmobile     | car   | trike |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Music-Genre: rock, trance, country, r&b
House: cottage, victorian, farmhouse, gothic-revival
1. Music-Genre:r&b == House:victorian##1
2. Music-Genre:rock is on the far right##1
3. Music-Genre:trance is on the right of Music-Genre:r&b##1
4. Music-Genre:r&b is on the right of House:farmhouse##1
5. House:victorian is on the left of House:cottage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | country | r&b | trance | rock    |
| House   | farmhouse    | victorian      | cottage | gothic-revival |

 #################################
 
